casebody.data:
177 A.3d 108 CMR CONSTRUCTION CORP., PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. ROBERTA GREENING, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-398 September Term 2017

080008 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004442-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
